1.What is Playwright?
Playwright is an open-source automation testing framework developed by Microsoft for end-to-end testing of web applications. It supports 
multiple browsers like Chromium, Firefox, and WebKit and provides features like auto-waiting, parallel execution, and built-in locators, 
which makes UI automation reliable and fast.

