For debugging and reporting, we use Playwright’s HTML reports, Trace Viewer, screenshots, and videos on failure, which helps quickly identify flaky or environment-specific issues.
The framework is integrated with CI/CD, running in headless mode with parallel execution on every code push. We retain traces and videos only for failed tests to keep CI fast.
